        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b12_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又長兼出大乘偷蘭之事。",
        "translation": "It's also a long commentary that gives an account of the great vehicle theft of the forest.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b12_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誡後人。",
        "translation": "He admonishes those who follow him.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b13_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有說言常翹一脚(至)當知是人是大菩薩。",
        "translation": "'If someone says, 'Always put one foot up,' you should know that person is a great bodhisattva.'",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b14_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b15_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "僧宗曰。",
        "translation": "The Saṃgha School says.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b15_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第七用若九十五種道。",
        "translation": "\"The seventh function is to define ninety-five paths.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b15_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "皆聽出家。",
        "translation": "They're all heard as renunciants.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b15_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦為亂律也。",
        "translation": "That's also a violation of the Vinaya.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b16_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "智秀曰。",
        "translation": "Zhixiu said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b16_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此第十一。",
        "translation": "\"This is the eleventh.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b16_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂佛聽畜不如法物。",
        "translation": "It means the Buddha hears about animals that are not like the Dharma.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b16_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及聽出家。",
        "translation": "He also listens to renunciant practitioners.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b17_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦為魔說也。",
        "translation": "It's also called the teaching of Māra.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b17_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子魔說佛說差別之相今已為汝廣宣分別。",
        "translation": "Good sons, Māra teaches the distinctive characteristics of Buddha's teachings, and now I've explained them in detail for you.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b18_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b19_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "智秀曰。",
        "translation": "Zhixiu said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b19_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "結上旨也。",
        "translation": "\"This concludes the above point.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b19_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "迦葉白佛言世尊我今始知(至)因是得入佛法深義。",
        "translation": "Kāśyapa said to the Buddha, \"Bhagavān, now I've come to know that this is the cause for realizing the profound meaning of the Buddha's teaching.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b20_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b21_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "智秀曰。",
        "translation": "Zhixiu said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b21_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "讚嘆。",
        "translation": "\"Hail!",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b21_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛讚迦葉善哉善哉(至)曉了分別是名黠慧。",
        "translation": "\"The Buddha praised Kāśyapa, 'Good, good!' (to) Understanding and discerning is called wisdom.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b22_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "案。",
        "translation": "Commentary.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b23_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "智秀曰。",
        "translation": "Zhixiu said.",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b23_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "述成也。",
        "translation": "'It's also described as accomplished.'",
        "source": "T37n1763_017:0445b23_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
